summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the proposal of Judkins Park Development Corporation to purchase and develop Parcel 32A in the I-90 Redevelopment Project area; authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to execute and deliver contracts and deeds; authorizing the Department of Housing and Human Services Director to execute, deliver and administer the "Contract for Sale of Land"; authorizing payment to the State of Washington of the purchase price owing; and designating the disposition of sales proceeds.
